cu.explanation_en: Setting amf_ip_address.ipv4 to '10.0.0.1', an unreachable IP address, causing CU to fail in connecting to the AMF due to routing misconfiguration.

du.explanation_en: Setting remote_s_address to '10.255.255.1', which is an unreachable IP address, causing SCTP connection failures due to routing issues.
du.explanation_zh: 将 remote_s_address 设置为 '10.255.255.1'，这是一个不可达的 IP 地址，导致由于路由问题而导致 SCTP 连接失败。
